IN the INTEREST OF L.F., Minor Child, S.F., Mother, Appellant. No. 17-0818 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed July 19, 2017

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother appeals the adjudication of her child as a child in need of assistance following a dispositional hearing. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
